This episode of HashiCast highlights Armon Dadgar from HashiCorp.

Armon Dadgar is one of the two founders and the co-CTO of HashiCorp. Armon has an immense passion for Open Source and distributed systems to solve real world problems. He has worked on Nomad, Vault, Terraform, Consul, and Serf at HashiCorp, and maintains the Statsite and Bloomd OSS projects as well.

We chat about how Armon got started with technology. We explored his early days in high school and university. We talked about how HashiCorp came into existence and the most challenging problems for HashiCorp as a company in the next few years. 

Guests: 
Armon Dadgar - HashiCorp

Hosts:
